  id: quest_jane_7
  questName: "Tak snadn\xE9, ale drah\xE9"
  required: 2
  reward: 1
  startOfQuest:
  - "T\xEDmhle questem, zahajuju te\u010F s\xE9rii 3 quest\u016F, kter\xE9 kdy\u017E
    spln\xED\u0161, tak ti umo\u017En\xEDm m\xEDt nasazen\xE9ho 4. peta."
  - "A prvn\xED quest nen\xED vubec slo\u017Eit\xFD. T\xEDm, \u017Ee se to bude odehr\xE1vata
    okolo pet\u016F, tak by to m\u011Blo i petama za\u010D\xEDt."
  - "Otev\u0159i 2 ciheln\xE9 vaj\xED\u010Dka. Nic v\xEDc, nic m\xED\u0148. Douf\xE1m,
    \u017Ee m\xE1\u0161 na\u0161et\u0159eno dostatek pen\u011Bz. Hodn\u011B \u0161t\u011Bst\xED."
  endOfQuest:
  - "Ber to tak, alespo\u0148 m\xE1\u0161 te\u010F snad siln\u011Bj\u0161\xED pety
    :). Ale odm\u011Bna bude velmi d\u016Fle\u017Eit\xE1."
  - "Tohle nejde z\xEDskat jen tak kde, tak\u017Ee si t\xE9hle nab\xEDdky va\u017E.
    Dal\u0161\xED quest se bude zase to\u010Dit okolo uk\xE1zky vesnice."
